ty-cover-Troye-Sivan-Radio-1-Live-Lounge-news.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《最后的晚宴》的阿比盖尔·莫里斯（左）和特洛伊·希文（右）的两张并排图像" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TheLastDinnerParty-cover-Troye-Sivan-Radio-1-Live-Lounge-news.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TheLastDinnerParty-cover-Troye-Sivan-Radio-1-Live-Lounge-news-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TheLastDinnerParty-cover-Troye-Sivan-Radio-1-Live-Lounge-news-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TheLastDinnerParty-cover-Troye-Sivan-Radio-1-Live-Lounge-news-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TheLastDinnerParty-cover-Troye-Sivan-Radio-1-Live-Lounge-news-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TheLastDinnerParty-cover-Troye-Sivan-Radio-1-Live-Lounge-news-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party</a>今天（2 月 6 日）在 BBC Radio 1 的 Live Lounge 首次亮相，翻唱了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/troye-sivan">Troye Sivan</a>的《One Of Your Girls》。请看下面。</p><p>今天下午，这支伦敦乐队在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/troye-sivan-something-to-give-each-other-lyrics-3513621">Sivan 的 2023 年单曲</a>中融入了令人难以忘怀的巴洛克流行风格，此前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/courtney-love-helped-the-last-dinner-party-censor-nothing-matters-lyrics-for-radio-radar-3576310">他们推出了首张单曲《Nothing Matters》的适合广播电台的现场版本</a>。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-the-last-dinner-party-interview-prelude-to-ecstasy-3552625">最后的晚宴：巴洛克流行音乐的新加冕君主</a></strong></li></ul><p>在解释封面选择时，主唱阿比加尔·莫里斯 (Abigal Morris) 表示，该乐队的贝斯手乔治亚·戴维斯 (Georgia Davies) “与特洛伊·希文 (Troye Sivan) 关系密切”。</p><p>戴维斯补充道：“我也是澳大利亚人，所以我是看着 Troye Sivan 长大的，看到澳大利亚同胞也在音乐游戏中取得成功真是太酷了。我只是觉得他很邪恶，我爱他。”</p><p>会后，The Last Evening Party 向 Radio 1 表示，他们的首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-last-dinner-party-prelude-to-ecstasy-album-review-radar-3577784">《Prelude To Ecstacy》</a>让他们“沉迷于情感和声音的极致”，并补充道：“这只是一场小小的盛宴。”</p><p>您可以<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/sounds/play/m001vrdh" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>收听完整的 Live Lounge 音乐和采访，并在下面观看乐队表演“One Of Your Girls”和“Nothing Matters”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="最后的晚宴 - One Of Your Girls（Troye Sivan 封面）在现场休息室" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/1hEVp4Guunk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="最后的晚宴——现场休息室里什么都不重要" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/5tCH8Pq5DjE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">喜欢这个封面<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2764-fe0f-200d-1f525.png" alt="❤️‍🔥" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://twitter.com/lastdinnerparty?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@lastdinnerparty</a>在<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/livelounge?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#livelounge</a>中表演<a href="https://twitter.com/troyesivan?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@troyesivan</a>的“one of your girls” <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2728.png" alt="✨" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p>在<a href="https://twitter.com/BBCSounds?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@bbcsounds</a>上收听完整内容<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f495.png" alt="💕" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://t.co/RPbrr2L9v3">https://t.co/RPbrr2L9v3</a> <a href="https://t.co/pwu3uui9lW">pic.twitter.com/pwu3uui9lW</a></p><p> — BBC 广播 1 台 (@BBCR1) <a href="https://twitter.com/BBCR1/status/1754843303298646368?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 2 月 6 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> The Last Evening Party 于上个月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-crowned-bbc-sound-of-2024-winners-3565767">荣获 BBC Sound Of 2024 民意调查获胜者</a>后，首次在 Live Lounge 首次亮相。 2023 年末，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-brits-announce-2024-rising-star-winner-3555457">该乐队荣获英国广播公司第一台 (BBC Radio 1) 支持的全英新星奖</a>。</p><p> <em>NME</em>在对上周五（2 月 2 日）发行的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-last-dinner-party-prelude-to-ecstasy-album-review-radar-3577784">《Prelude To Ecstacy》的四星评论</a>中将这张专辑描述为“华丽、有趣且完全独特”，并补充说它充满了“美妙的歌曲”。</p><p>唱片到达的前一天晚上， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/the-last-dinner-party-live-in-london-setlist-photos-3581176">《最后的晚宴》在伦敦卡姆登镇的圆屋举行了一场头条秀</a>。目前，乐队正在进行一系列英国唱片店的演出。 </p><figure id="attachment_3577791" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3577791" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3577791" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-last-dinner-party-band.jpg" alt="最后的晚宴" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-last-dinner-party-band.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-last-dinner-party-band-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-last-dinner-party-band-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-last-dinner-party-band-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-last-dinner-party-band-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-last-dinner-party-band-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3577791" class="wp-caption-text">最后的晚宴。图片来源：NME 的菲比·福克斯</figcaption></figure><p>继<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-announce-2024-european-tour-dates-buy-tickets-3531799">欧洲</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-announce-extensive-2024-us-tour-buy-tickets-3575005">北美</a>的预定演出之后，他们将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-announce-uk-and-ireland-tour-dates-for-2024-buy-tickets-3578583">九月开始英国和爱尔兰的头条巡演</a>。您可以<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/the-last-dinner-party-tickets/artist/5395177?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=wwEzBLW-RxyPWNIXqSXj8x-BUkHwpGXeiX3SU00&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>找到英国/爱尔兰音乐会的剩余门票。</p><p>此外，《最后的晚餐派对》将于 2024 年在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-2024-fontaines-d-c-renee-rapp-pendulum-among-50-new-names-added-to-line-up-3580742">Reading &amp; Leeds</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/trnsmt-2024-liam-gallagher-gerry-cinmamon-calvin-harris-lead-line-up-3545593">TRNSMT</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coachella-2024-line-up-lana-del-rey-tyler-the-creator-doja-cat-no-doubt-3571866">Coachella</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/primavera-sound-announce-stacked-line-up-for-2024-3545261">Primavera Sound</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/foo-fighters-and-dua-lipa-announced-as-rock-werchter-2024-headliners-3537761">Rock Werchter</a>上亮相。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-last-dinner-party-cover-troye-sivans-one-of-your-girls-in-the-radio-1-live-lounge-nme-radar-3583280">在 Radio 1 Live Lounge 中观看 The Last Evening Party 翻唱 Troye Sivan 的歌曲《One Of Your Girls》后，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
